---
layout: team-layout.njk
title: LG 트윈스
teamCss: team-lg.css
category: lg
---

<div class="team-analysis">
 <h2>LG 트윈스에 대한 분석</h2>
<p>우측은 사견, 좌측은 분석글 목록!</p>
</div>

{% set filteredPosts = collections.teamPosts | filter(attr => attr.data.category == category) %}
<ul class="team-post-list">
  {% for post in filteredPosts %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      <span class="date">{{ post.date | date }}</span>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>